### âœ… Key Changes

| Type         | Description                                                       |
|--------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------|
| â™»ï¸ Script     | New script to compare issues in all matching repos across orgs    |
| ðŸ›¡ï¸ Error Handling | Handles auth, missing repos, malformed tokens, and API errors     |
| ðŸ“Š Output     | Generates a CSV report logging any issue number mismatches        |
| ðŸ” Comparison | Checks for issues missing on **either** side (source & destination) |

