### ðŸ§ª Output Sample

| Repository      | Direction             | Missing Issue Number |
|-----------------|-----------------------|-----------------------|
| `repo-a`        | `missing_in_destination` | 42                    |
| `repo-a`        | `missing_in_source`      | 19                    |
| `repo-b`        | `missing_in_destination` | 8                     |

> Output written to: `missing_issues_report.csv`

